{"tid":1420725,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"提防分化撚，勇武唔撚割，和理非都唔撚割","createTime":"2019-08-06T05:37:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T06:48:43.000Z","uid":264455,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"60e92048a6d83fe5aad6b421208d7e7a64b09f96","tid":1420725,"uid":264455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:37:02.000Z","msg":"/林鄭開始明白，政府和警察之前的失敗，是因為他們的所作所為，令得他們道德破產，因而不再得到人們的信任和尊重。而他們學得很快，正在努力嘗試用新的論述和政治公關來說服香港人：他們才是對的一方，因此他們對抗爭者的鎮壓，是合理的，是值得香港人支持的。而我們，沒有理由如此容易受騙及墮入這個陷阱。<br />\n<br />\n因此，<span style=\"color: gold;\">千萬不要輕視觀念和道德的力量，同時在行動時也須盡最大努力爭取最多人的認可和支持</span>/<br />\n<br />\n/這套論述如果能夠打動香港人（當然不需要所有），整個社會輿論就會改變，這場轟轟烈烈、浩浩蕩蕩的香港自由之夏運動很可能就會受到嚴重挫折。<br />\n<br />\n讀者或會問，一套論述無論說得多麼動聽，如果本身沒有合理性及沒有社會基礎支持，從而得到香港人的認可，它就不可能具有正當化的力量（legitimation force）。<br />\n<br />\n是的，確實如此。一套政治論述的正當化過程，往往就是在公共場域中，訴諸人們的道德價值和道德情感的證成過程。<span style=\"color: gold;\">林鄭政府在接著下來，必然會動用各種可能的手段，來令大家相信她的這套論述（包括每天的記招）的合理性</span>。/<br />\n<br />\n周保松〈論林鄭的新論述〉<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%AB%96%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E7%9A%84%E6%96%B0%E8%AB%96%E8%BF%B0/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25AB%2596%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%25AB%2596%25E8%25BF%25B0%2F&d=NNqT6wnuCkALqD5scUUSnCWBa%2BgBXVTVyFCVgu0cTpM%3D&h=c731aec0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25AB%2596%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%25AB%2596%25E8%25BF%25B0%2F&h=665e4dd2\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%AB%96%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E7%9A%84%E6%96%B0%E8%AB%96%E8%BF%B0/</a><br />\n<br />\n林鄭一轉策略，馬上愈嚟愈多分化post<br />\n一係割勇武，一係割和理非<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">目的係想自己友打自己友</span></span><br />\n千祈唔好咁易俾人帶風向，唔好意氣用事<br />\n<br />\n大局為重，輿論戰啱啱先開始<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">記住得民心者得天下！！</span>"},{"pid":"bcad15a94dd5aa2f754bad9fdc1cf2a14cc2b2e5","tid":1420725,"uid":201438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:38:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6152a1c84f8c99ae4b110028961d6d929dbd7b74","tid":1420725,"uid":264455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:39:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f1c81aefa250069612cd2b37b5e8222ad543e2b","tid":1420725,"uid":120555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:41:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4a89079204d8a824d6c6a8712dd8291225598d34","tid":1420725,"uid":264455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:42:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2b7c8a731ff15d85e1eeccc9f3875a96008705e6","tid":1420725,"uid":264455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:42:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d909a5d6e296da2961a1dd0fa027514aee7d7032","tid":1420725,"uid":253833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:03:42.000Z","msg":"［借acc][純建議] 8月24日 全港罷買日 搞「靜」香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1420749\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1420749</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6569fc1e3b5a0348919f9e4604b923909d1e9036","tid":1420725,"uid":253833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:48:43.000Z","msg":"和理非入一入來唔該<br />\n［借acc][純建議] 8月24日 全港罷買日 搞「靜」香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1420749\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1420749</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}